OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Fsome showery rain at first but this
OL,7,Fsoon clearing east in the evening. A
OL,8,Fdry start to the night then some cloud
OL,9,Fand rain will spread northeast later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FA mainly dry and bright
OL,12,Fmorning in the east. Otherwise, cloudy
OL,13,Fand breezy throughout the day as
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain move northeast,
OL,15,Fthese heavy at times.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,18,For sunny spells and scattered showers
OL,19,Ffrom Monday to Wednesday, heavy and
OL,20,Fthundery at times.
